1lb Almonds, Cold Smoked for 4 hours
- or 
1lb Cashews, Cold Smoked for 1.5/2 hours 

2.5 Tablespoons Olive Oil (I use garlic olive oil) 
1/4 teaspoon cayenne pepper
1/2 teaspoon garlic powder 
1 Tablespoon finely ground kosher or sea salt 
2 teaspoons chili powder
1 teaspoon black pepper 

Heat in oven at 350 for 10-15 mins stirring a few tiems.
